org.fife.ui.search

Interface ResultsComponent


  • interface ResultsComponent
    Interface that identifies a component that displays search or replace information in a FindInFilesDialog or ReplaceInFilesDialog.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Robert Futrell

    • Method Summary

      Returns the number of rows displayed in this component.
